generated_description: pirracchio, legally known as max-planck-strasse pirracchio gbr, is a family-owned company based in metzingen, baden-württemberg. the company specializes in metalworking and heat treatment services, offering a range of processes including quenching, carburizing, martensitic heat treatment, bainitic intermediate heat treatment, and nitriding. pirracchio also provides metalworking services such as deburring, sawing, grinding, and welding, including mig welding. the company is certified under din iso standards and emphasizes high-quality processes and documentation.
